column2: SELECT ph.ra,ph.dec    From PhotoObj ph, MyDB.redmapper1 p, dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(p.ra,p.#dec,p.#SearchRadius) as match1    /*Join MyDB.redmapper1 p ON dbo.fGetNearestObjIdAllEq(p.ra,p.#dec,p.#SearchRadius).objID = redmapper1.objID   JOIN dbo.fGetNearestObjIdAllEq(p.ra,p.#dec,p.#SearchRadius) match1 ON ph.objID = match1.objID*/    where    ph.petroMag_i< p.#i
